u_{t}-(u_{t})_{x}+(b+1)uu_{x}=bu_{x}u_{xx}+uu_{xxx}
\hat{u}_{t}-(i\omega)^{2}\hat{u}_{t}=\hat{F}(u)
F(u)=bu_{x}u_{xx}-(b+1)uu_{x}+uu_{xxx}
\hat{u}_{t}=\frac{\hat{F}(u)}{1+\omega^{2}}
